			<h3>Features</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Interactive hotspot markers on images</li>
				<li>Customizable position using percentage coordinates</li>
				<li>Rich content support including HTML and links</li>
				<li>Custom icons for visual differentiation</li>
				<li>Responsive design that scales with image</li>
				<li>Hover and click interactions</li>
				<li>Accessible markup with proper ARIA labels</li>
				<li>Smooth animations and transitions</li>
			</ul>

